# ── iCloud / Finder duplicate artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────
# This repo lives in an iCloud-synced folder, which periodically forks files as
# "<name> 2.ext", "<name> 3.ext", … These are NEVER real source. Verified at add
# time that NO tracked file matches this pattern, so committed files are unaffected
# (.gitignore only hides untracked files). The real fix is to move the repo out of
# iCloud Drive — these rules are a stopgap so the dupes stop reappearing in status.
* [2-9].swift
* [2-9].md
* [2-9].plist
* [2-9].json
* [2-9].entitlements
* [2-9].storyboard
* [2-9].pbxproj
* [2-9].h
* [2-9].m
.gitignore [2-9]
